# Output — valid JSON only, no prose, no markdown fences

Respond with a JSON object keyed by the same indices above:

```json
{
  "verdicts": [
    {"index": 1, "verdict": "yes", "reason": "Staff PM in AI/ML platform"},
    {"index": 2, "verdict": "no", "reason": "intern role"},
    {"index": 3, "verdict": "maybe", "reason": "PM function but domain unclear"}
  ]
}
```

Rules:
- Every input index MUST be represented in `verdicts`
- `verdict` MUST be exactly one of `"yes"`, `"no"`, `"maybe"`
- `reason` MUST be ≤ 12 words, matter-of-fact
- Output ONLY the JSON object
